# Project Context

Stack: Python 3.12, aiogram 3, Qdrant, PostgreSQL, OpenClaw sidecar, Docker Compose on vps-tw-server 83.217.220.3

## Key rules
- All secrets from environment variables only
- All DB access through parameterized queries (no f-strings in SQL)
- Bot handlers must be fully async (asyncpg, aiohttp, qdrant-client async)
- Crawler is the only component that writes to PostgreSQL
- Qdrant chunks are immutable after indexing — never update, only add new version chunks
- Status logic (current/future/archive) lives in crawler only

## Commands
- Check: `./scripts/check.sh`
- Crawler: `./scripts/run-crawler.sh`
- Indexer: `./scripts/run-indexer.sh`
- Deploy: `./scripts/deploy.sh` — SSH to vps-tw-server, docker compose up -d

